if you wanna want it work follow these instructions
1. Disconnect from the Internet.

2. Install the trial version of Sony Vegas Pro 9.0 (32-bit or 64-bit).

3. Do not open Sony Vegas.

4. Move the Keygen from your download folder to the newly installed Vegas Pro 9.0 folder (usually C:\Program Files\Sony\Sony Vegas 9.0).

5. Run the Keygen (If using Vista or 7, right click the keygen and click "RUN AS ADMINISTRATOR").

6. Select Vegas Pro 9.0 (32 and 64 bit) Series.

7. Click "Generate".

8. Click "Patch" and select the destination folder that Sony Vegas was installed to (Usually C:\Program Files\Sony\Vegas Pro 9.0).

9. Run Sony Vegas.

10. Copy and Paste the serial number and click "Next".

11. Select "Register from another computer".

12. Use bullshit information and save anywhere.

12. Copy and paste the Authentication Code from the Keygen

13. Click Finish
